<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_41" id="20v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_41_r1l5">Heıncʒen vvychſenſteiner </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_41_r1l6"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>vvychſenſtein<ex>er</ex></expan> . als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von der nom <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_41_r1l7">den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>beſcheh<ex>en</ex></expan> ıſt . dabey Jr geweſen ſeyt Vnd darauf eins </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_41_r1l8">geleıts von vns begert auf ſand Lorencʒen tag ſchıerıſt etc das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_41_r1l9"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> Vnd wenn Jr <expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd ſand <expan>lorencʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_41_r1l10">tag ſchıerıſt ʒu vns kombt vnd des <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> . ſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır ewch vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_41_r1l11"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>̈n</expan> <expan>knecht<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe mıt eẅch reıten . 
<del rend="strikethrough"> vier tag </del> ʒu vns bey vns vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_41_r1l12"><expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> von vns . vıer tag ein geleıt <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . für vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_41_r1l13">on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> vnd <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><gap reason="illegible"/></del> denn eẅr rede <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> vt <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_41" id="20v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Heinczen Wychsensteiner </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Wychsenstein<ex>er</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von der nom
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>bescheh<ex>en</ex></expan> ist, dabey ir gewesen seyt und darauf eins
                        geleits von uns begert auf <app><note><q type="date">sand Lorenczen tag schierist</q>10.08.1414</note></app> etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und wenn ir
                                <expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan> und sand
                                <expan>Lorencze<ex>n</ex></expan> tag schierist zu uns kombt und des
                                <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan>, so <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir ewch und <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>̈n</expan>
<expan>knecht<ex>en</ex></expan>, die mit ewch reiten, zu uns, bey uns und
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> von uns vier tag ein geleit
                                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> für uns und die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan> und
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> denn ewr rede
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
